TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Look up on Day_Dimension to get AS_OF_DATE
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DAY_DIMENSION

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE as AS_OF_DATE, TRUNC(DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE) as DAY_DATE, 1 as DUMMY FROM DAY_DIMENSION WHERE TRUNC(DAY_DIMENSION.DAY_DATE) =TRUNC(SYSDATE-7)

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Source query to fetch records with Process_flag='N'
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.DEMAND_WEEKEND_DATE, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.PLANT, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.DEMAND_TYPE, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.STYLE, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.COLOR, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.ATTRIBUTE_CD, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.SIZE_CD, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.CURRENT_QTY, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.PLAN_DATE, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.SCHEDULE_METHOD, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.SCHEDULE_RUN, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.PRIORITY_SEQUENCE, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.DEMAND_DRIVER, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.DEMAND_SOURCE, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.RULE_NUMBER, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.ATTRIBUTION_IND, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.CUSTOMER_SHIP_DATE, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.CRITICAL_RATIO, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.SPREAD_CRITICAL_RATIO, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.DUE_IN_DC_DATE, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.CEG_CODE, STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW.DEMAND_CLASS FROM STG_DPR_FCST_DEMAND_VIEW WHERE PROCESS_FLAG='N'

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Look up on item table to get the ITEM_ID
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT MIN(ITEM.ITEM_ID) as ITEM_ID, ITEM.SIZE_CODE as SIZE_CODE, ITEM.STYLE_NUM as STYLE_NUM, ITEM.ATTRIBUTION_CODE as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, ITEM.COLOR_CODE as COLOR_CODE FROM ITEM where division_group='slsp' AND item_type_code ='SEL' GROUP BY ITEM.SIZE_CODE , ITEM.STYLE_NUM , ITEM.ATTRIBUTION_CODE, ITEM.COLOR_CODE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SIZE_CODE = I_SIZE_CD AND STYLE_NUM = I__STYLE AND ATTRIBUTION_CODE = I_ATTRIBUTE_CD AND COLOR_CODE = I_COLOR
